20:52.418 --> 20:53.919
pins that aren't lining up.

20:53.919 --> 20:54.962
‐ Yep.

20:54.962 --> 20:56.088
‐ What do you know?

20:56.088 --> 20:57.423
It doesn't fit up.

20:57.423 --> 20:58.424
<i>[frantic rock music]</i>

20:58.424 --> 20:59.800
<i>If I end up not getting</i>

20:59.800 --> 21:01.093
<i>these two pieces of wood</i>

21:01.093 --> 21:03.262
<i>and the pins to all line up,</i>

21:03.262 --> 21:04.305
I'm probably gonna go home.

