Everything is out of whack.

21:08.768 --> 21:10.436
<i>I have to realign my holes,</i>

21:10.436 --> 21:12.229
<i>and truthfully,</i>
<i>I'm just gonna drill</i>

21:12.229 --> 21:13.606
these holes bigger

21:13.606 --> 21:14.607
[grinding]

21:14.607 --> 21:15.816
so that they can fit

21:15.816 --> 21:18.027
any pinstock that I shove
in there.

21:18.027 --> 21:19.820
‐ All right.
