in half

23:52.932 --> 23:53.933
when he hits the bamboo.

23:57.102 --> 24:00.147
[grunting aggressively
with each strike]

24:00.147 --> 24:03.275
<i>[aggressive rock music]</i>

24:03.275 --> 24:10.282
<i>♪ ♪</i>

24:10.282 --> 24:11.784
‐ Nice job, Colton.

24:11.784 --> 24:12.952
The edge held up well.

24:12.952 --> 24:14.954
You fixed that little warp,

24:14.954 --> 24:16.622
so everything stayed lined up.

24:16.622 --> 24:18.290
The handle I would have liked

24:18.290 --> 24:19.959
to have been beefed up
a little bit.

24:19.959 --> 24:21.293
It's on the narrow side.

24:21.293 --> 24:24.964
But overall, good job.
‐ Thank you.

24:24.964 --> 24:26.966
‐ Hey, Bryce. How you doin'?
‐ Doing good.

24:26.966 --> 24:29.134
‐ You gonna make Big Blu proud?
‐ I am.

24:29.134 --> 24:30.177
‐ Let's see.

24:30.177 --> 24:31.470
<i>[intense music]</i>

24:31.470 --> 24:32.846
<i>‐ Soon as J. grabs my blade,</i>

24:32.846 --> 24:34.974
<i>I'm just like, "Wow."</i>

24:34.974 --> 24:36.642
<i>I'm worried my blade's</i>
<i>a little bit thin,</i>

24:36.642 --> 24:38.268
<i>so I'm hoping that</i>
<i>it doesn't crack</i>

24:38.268 --> 24:39.812
or splinter off.

24:39.812 --> 24:42.773
[grunting with each strike]

24:42.773 --> 24:45.985
<i>[heavy metal bass riff]</i>

24:45.985 --> 24:49.029
<i>♪ ♪</i>

24:52.324 --> 24:54.076
‐ Nice work, Bryce.

24:54.076 --> 24:56.078
It's not the prettiest knife
I've ever seen,

24:56.078 --> 24:58.163
but your edge held up fine.

24:58.163 --> 25:01.500
Your handle? A little bit long,
kind of simple.

25:01.500 --> 25:04.336
But, overall, good job.
‐ Thank you.

25:04.336 --> 25:06.755
‐ And then there was Craig.
How you feeling, bud?

25:06.755 --> 25:08.215
‐ I'm feeling good.
I'm ready to go.

25:08.215 --> 25:09.883
‐ All right, well let's see
how your knife feels.

25:09.883 --> 25:11.969
‐ Let's do it.

25:11.969 --> 25:14.680
<i>As I watch the other tests</i>
<i>going on,</i>

25:14.680 --> 25:16.557
<i>I'm just kind of getting</i>
<i>more amped up.</i>

25:16.557 --> 25:18.058
<i>I'm ready for it,</i>

25:18.058 --> 25:21.353
but you cannot make
those butterflies settle down.

25:21.353 --> 25:22.938
<i>♪ ♪</i>

25:22.938 --> 25:26.025
[loud grunting
with each strike]

25:26.025 --> 25:32.990
<i>♪ ♪</i>

25:35.701 --> 25:37.578
‐ It survived!
