27:06.208 --> 27:08.502
and there's a little bit
big space right there,

27:08.502 --> 27:10.295
but most of all, sir,

27:10.295 --> 27:11.296
it will cut.

27:11.296 --> 27:12.923
‐ Thank you.

27:12.923 --> 27:14.800
‐ All right, old‐timer.
