27:14.800 --> 27:15.968
You ready for this?

27:15.968 --> 27:18.804
‐ I'm as ready as I'm getting.
‐ Let's do this.

27:18.804 --> 27:19.805
<i>‐ The first two blades go</i>

27:19.805 --> 27:21.807
<i>and they slice perfectly,</i>

27:21.807 --> 27:23.809
<i>and all I'm expecting to see</i>

27:23.809 --> 27:27.604
