<i>is really gonna affect</i>
<i>its performance.</i>

31:04.321 --> 31:05.530
<i>[energetic rock music]</i>

31:05.530 --> 31:07.032
It's just about there.

31:07.032 --> 31:09.451
We'll get it up
just a little bit more.

31:09.451 --> 31:10.702
<i>I'm heating up my bow.</i>

31:10.702 --> 31:11.787
<i>The heat's looking even.</i>

31:11.787 --> 31:13.205
<i>It's looking pretty good.</i>

31:13.205 --> 31:14.372
I think I'm gonna
go for it.

31:14.372 --> 31:16.875
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:16.875 --> 31:20.712
<i>We're in, and no pops,</i>
<i>no cracks.</i>

31:20.712 --> 31:22.214
I'm feeling good about it
right now.

31:22.214 --> 31:23.548
[scraping]

31:23.548 --> 31:25.383
Oh, yeah. See that? That's‐‐
